# FILE: adminDashboard/UniversalOrderManager/UniversalOrderManager.desc
# ROLE: Financial Fulfillment & Escrow Release Hub
# ROUTE: /admin/orders
# ACCOUNT: Admin only
# THEME: Dark · high-stakes tabular · mission-control

## 1. ESCROW AUTHORIZATION QUEUE (Freelance — Top Priority)
- CARD STYLE: border-[#F59E0B]/30 · bg-[#F59E0B]/5 (amber alert) — pulsing border
- SOURCE: from /dashboard/contracts (student-side approval)
- COLUMNS: Project Name · Freelancer Type (student/external) · Student Approval Status · Escrow Amount
- ACTIONS:
  - [💸 إتمام الصرف] — releases ShamCash from platform escrow to freelancer wallet
  - [🛑 تجميد الأموال] — used when dispute is opened

## 2. STORE FULFILLMENT TRACKER
- SOURCE: from /dashboard/orders
- DATA: Order ID · Customer Name · Item · Verification Status · Amount
- THE HANDSHAKE: "Secure Pickup Code" entry field
  - Admin/broker enters student's 4-digit PIN
  - On match: status auto-updates to ✅ مُستلم for both admin and student

## 3. VENDOR ORDER MANAGEMENT (Business Accounts)
- Orders placed for products from businessType === 'vendor' accounts
- Same columns as store tracker + Vendor Name column
- Vendor notified via inbox when order is placed

## 4. PHYSICAL DISPATCH BOARD
- Items ready for pickup today (sorted by time)
- BROKER ASSIGNMENT: dropdown to assign team member to pickup node
- [📤 إشعار الطالب] — sends "جاهز للاستلام" to student's system inbox

## 5. CANCELLATION & REFUND LOGIC
- [🗑️ إلغاء الطلب] → auto-credits virtual wallet on student side
- All cancellations timestamped with reason

## 6. FILTER & SEARCH
- Search by: Order ID · Student UID · Freelancer Name · Vendor Name
- FILTERS: 🕒 قيد الانتظار · 📦 في الطريق · 💰 في الضمان · ✅ مكتمل

## 7. STICKY SUMMARY HUD
- "إجمالي الضمان: 4,500,000 SYP" | "طلبات جاهزة: 12"
- MANTRA: "اقتصاد بلا تسرب — Challenge Every Day."
